Query: This is to complain about the late delivery of my above order on Sept. 24th. By 3-4 hours!  I was in contact with Mr. Anish/Takeaway about this from Sept. 18th, and confirmed my requirement on the 21st evening. Pre-payment was completed 22nd evening, and final details agreed 23rd morning, for delivery to my residence 24th afternoon 3-4pm. However, on not receiving any update from you till 4:30pm on the 24th, I had to start ignoring our guests and chasing you, first Mr. Anish (who seemed to be off-duty and completely unaware of my order's status), and then desperately through your other phone Nos.  The cake, Raan, etc. finally arrived at 7pm!! By which time most of our guests, children and parents had already left our birthday party. As a result, a part of the cake is still in our fridge, unfinished.  Apologies were received by WhatsApp, and a card/box of chocolates with the delivery. Little consolation for the embarrassment our family went through, and are still feeling. After waiting a week for some further sign of regret from you (which has not come), I am hereby registering my formal complaint.   Late Sh. YC Deveshwar and I are alumni of the same institution (IIT-Delhi, he was senior to me). My family and I have loyalty to your group, my wedding events were held at ITC Maurya-Delhi in 1982, and over the decades we’ve regularly ordered from Fabelle, Bukhara and Peshawri in New Delhi, Chennai and Mumbai. However, after this last bad experience I wonder if we can rely on you again. Clearly my (pre-paid) order in your system was completely forgotten, and only began being processed after I followed-up on the 24th late afternoon!  A further issue is your charging Delivery Charges extra this time, which was earlier always included in bill amounts over 4-5k.  Therefore I expect you to immediately reverse your cake Invoice of Rs. 3,900/-, and Delivery Charges 500/-, and credit me Rs. 4,400/- against my next order, if you want me, my family and friends to continue feeling our old relationship with you. Otherwise I will circulate details of this shameful episode to your corporate offices, etc.  Kindly let me have your response today.  Regards.
